    "headline": "SLB OneSubsea Awarded Integrated EPC Contract for Deepwater Development",
    "summary": "HOUSTON, March 17, 2026--Global energy technology company SLB (NYSE: SLB) announced today that its OneSubsea™ joint venture has been awarded a multi-well, integrated engineering, production, and construction (EPC) contract by China National Offshore Oil Corporation (CNOOC). The contract encompasses 20 wells and covers the delivery of integrated subsea production systems for the deepwater Kaiping 18-1 field development in the South China Sea.",
